Traditional detection methods fail to identify zero-day attacks and cannot adapt to evolving 
threat patterns.

RESEARCH OBJECTIVES
1. Develop a phishing detection model specifically for the financial sector
2. Implement online learning for real-time detection and adaptation
3. Detect zero-day phishing attacks targeting financial institutions
4. Create usable software for URL-based phishing detection

MY CONTRIBUTION
- Financial-specific feature engineering (bank keywords, urgency terms, etc.)
